parameters.name: DestinationCidrBlock
parameters.description: The destination CIDR block of the route entry in the gateway route table.

parameters.name: GatewayRouteTableId
parameters.description: The ID of the gateway route table that you want to query.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Valid values: **1** to **100**. Default value: **10**.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description:
The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results. Valid values:

*   You do not need to specify this parameter for the first request.
*   If a value is returned for NextToken, specify the value in the next request to retrieve a new page of results.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description:
The region ID of the gateway route table.

You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~36063~~) operation to query the most recent list of regions.
